# Path to a local Obsidian vault used during development. When set and the
# build script is run with `--vault` (e.g. `pnpm dev:vault` / `pnpm build:vault`),
# `main.js` and `manifest.json` are copied into
#   $TEST_VAULT/.obsidian/plugins/obsidian-team/
# after each build, so you can hot-reload the plugin in Obsidian.
TEST_VAULT=D:\DEV\Claude\ObsidianTeams\test-vault
